item.title: Fire at South Korea battery plant kills at least 16 people: Report
item.description: A fire that broke out at a South Korean lithium battery plant has killed at least 16 people, with five others missing, Reuters reported.

item.title: 20 Bodies Found As Fire Breaks Out In S Korea Battery Factory: Report
item.description: Around 20 bodies have been found at a South Korean lithium battery factory after a massive blaze on Monday, the Yonhap news agency said, with firefighters saying they were still searching the building.

item.title: Tons of robot vacuums also mop, but these 6 hybrids ace the job
item.description: The best robot vacuum mop combos do more than drag a soggy cloth around. We tested these hybrids from Roborock, Shark, and more.
